致對外！！"},{"pid":"1a8274b45491967474ecdf522b1bd504ead2d2f9","tid":1457313,"uid":94502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:38:33.000Z","msg":"關心唔代表可以放棄理智"},{"pid":"67ed6494c31e2b789aa6a5de6747d99c483bf386","tid":1457313,"uid":280436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:38:33.000Z","msg":"政府<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">操縱緊我地嘅言論</span></span>去<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">分化</span></span>勇武同和理非<br />\n<br />\n大量網軍混入連登，Facebook，telegram<br />\n散播謠言<br />\n令大家<span style=\"color: red;\">質疑</span>盟友嘅可信性<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">互相猜忌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果散</span> <br />\n就發表大量<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌撚散水狗</span></span></span>嘅言論<br />\n馬後砲<br />\n指責班合理擔心安全嘅和理非<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">be water</span></span>係大家一直以來重視嘅嘢<br />\n根本勇武唔會怪責<br />\n可見係政府故意引起割席<br />\n<br />\n如果<span style=\"color: red;\">唔散</span><br />\n警察真係做嘢<br />\n就會湧現和理非怪責勇武嘅言論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一切 都係政府設下嘅套路！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日真係有取消/延誤航班 <br />\n警察真係有佈防 而且有機會用得到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但真正目的並非實質行動<br />\n而係分化大家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最近安插臥底係前線同樣<br />\n都有一層目的係為左令尼場運動嘅參與者<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自行瓦解</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家千奇唔好中佢嘅計</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">謹記 不分化 不割席</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢嘅陰濕招數 我地只要團結 一定搵到方法破解<br />\n<br />\n幫手發表！ 自由修改"},{"pid":"b76fedf35fa8f209b095f8da9ae3c6dcc950ea4b","tid":1457313,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a8274b454919674